            <div class="opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper ">

    
    <h1 class="opener__hed " >        A Security Camera Caught an Employee Beating a Patient. It Took 11 Days for Anyone to Take Action.
    </h1>

    <h2 class="opener__dek " >        After our investigation revealed patient abuse at Illinois’ Choate Mental Health and Developmental Center, the facility installed cameras to help. But the footage isn’t monitored unless there’s an allegation of misconduct.
    </h2>

    </div> <!-- Close .opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper -->

</div>
        
<div class="article-meta-1
